data.description: Gorgeous Lake Views! No HOA! Come check out this lake home that's perfect for a weekend getaway, a longterm homestead, or a turn key rental - short term rental like airbnb is permitted! Main home consists of 2 bedrooms on the upper level with the main bath, as well as kitchen, living room, dining area, and study nook. On the lower level you have an additional living/sleeping quarters, full bathroom, laundry and storage. Enjoy sunrise mornings or calm evenings on the wrap around porch. The detached garage is where opportunity abounds! One half of the lower section was converted into a game room, while the other half is still functional as storage or workshop space. Upstairs is an unfinished garage apartment so get creative! You could house a long term tenant, have additional sleep space with a short term rental, live there and rent out the main home, or a variety of other possibilites. Situated on a 1/2 acre lot with RV parking and 50 amp hookup, space to store a boat, have bonfires and just a short drive to the boat ramp. Roof is less than 5 years old, well maintained, sold furnished and ready to go!
